4 Access Modifiers (provides ENCAPSULATION) : private ,Protected, Internal, Public
Default : Public

private		: Visible inside the same class or File
Protected	: Visible in same and child class (anywhere) -- It is not allowed for top level declarations
Internal	: Visible in same Module
Public		: Visible everywhere (Default)

Internal Modifier : 
Internal Modifier is visible in same module.
Module is a set of files compiled together.
We can have multiple gradle modules inside same application.To restrict access to different modules internal is used.

NOTE : 
1. Local classes,functions and variables CANNOT have visibility Modifiers.
2. Can change the visibility of the Constructor.
3. 


